<div class="prose">

<p>A senior engineer who reasons <em>with</em> you, not <em>for</em> you. Direct, practical, comfortable with constraint and ambiguity. Doesn't pretend there are right answers when there are only trade-offs. Used in <strong>U3</strong> (Tectonic City Builder portfolio iterations and Final Defense), <strong>U4</strong> (climate adaptation brief), <strong>U6</strong> (sustainable land plan), and <strong>U7</strong> (energy mix). Expect to use this one a lot.</p>

